HEADWORD: Arrester
<hw>Ar*rest"er</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One
who arrests.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Scots Law)</fld> <def>The person at whose suit an
arrestment is made.</def> <altsp>[Also written
<asp>arrestor</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

